  "invariants": [
    "Citation v2 phai hydrate canonical text tu LegalProvision trong Neo4j bang provision_id; vector KHONG phai nguon trich dan.",
    "LegalProvision text is immutable: same provision_id with a different text_checksum must be rejected.",
    "Normal ingest cannot change effective_from, effective_to, source_vb_id or source_checksum of an existing LegalProvision.",
    "Only an approved amendment commit may close effective_to or create SUPERSEDED_BY.",
    "Temporal interval is half-open: effective_from <= as_of < effective_to; null effective_to means open-ended.",
    "SUPERSEDED_BY only connects versions with the same lineage_id and level, and must not form a cycle.",
    "Citizen chi doc VanBanPhapLuat.visibility='public' va BaiTomTat.status='published' (filter o BE3).",
    "Canh GAN_CO_CAN_KIEM_CHUNG bat buoc co score + method.",
    "Canh DOI_CHIEU.label thuoc {khop, mau_thuan, khong_ro}.",
    "Misconception clustering requires an exact source evidence span, canonical URL, content checksum and a high-confidence contradictory DOI_CHIEU occurrence.",
    "OUTDATED_BUT_PREVIOUSLY_TRUE requires a historical KHOP basis and a different current MAU_THUAN physical version on the same lineage, with both immutable LegalProvision checksums.",
    "Misconception source_count and risk velocity/diversity use distinct content_hash values so syndicated copies count once.",
    "MERGE idempotent: replay same source/text checksum -> same provision_id; conflicts require review."
  ],
  "audit_note": "PUBLISHED_AS (BaiTomTat) duoc ghi audit o Postgres (bang audit_log/briefs), khong bat buoc la canh Neo4j."
